original_title: Billy Blanks' Tae Bo: Fat Blasting Cardio
overview: Get your heart pumping with this ultra-effective cardio workout, and Billy will guide you on your way to a complete flab-meltdown. He takes you through the TAE BO-based signature workouts that have enlisted people all over the world, working with you every step of the way while his one-of-a-kind moves and can't-stay-still music generate a brand-new you in record time!
title: Billy Blanks' Tae Bo: Fat Blasting Cardio
